{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "第十八回\"一日数惊\"讲述了李寻欢在被押送少林途中接连遭遇追杀的惊险经历。伊哭（青魔手）为报徒弟丘独之仇拦截心眉大师一行，李寻欢在穴道被封、仅能发一柄飞刀的情况下重伤伊哭将其击退，展现出小李飞刀的惊人威力。田七此前暗中解开李寻欢臂部穴道并提供飞刀，实为借刀杀人之计。随后众人投宿客栈，菜中竟被下毒，四名少林僧人中毒身亡。李寻欢辨认出下毒者为苗疆极乐峒主五毒童子，此人善用蛇虫之毒杀人于无形。此后一路之上五毒童子不断变换下毒方式——馍馍中有毒而面汤里有解药、油煎饼无毒但专为目标而设——防不胜防。田七灵机一动，以油煎饼向路边贫童换取无毒的面饽饽，终于得以饱餐一顿。全章以\"一日数惊\"为题，将伊哭强攻、五毒暗害、尔虞我诈的江湖险恶展现得淋漓尽致。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "外面有人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "伊哭！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来是找我的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "青魔手也是你的朋友？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜这朋友也像我别的朋友一样，就想要我的脑袋。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "伊檀越？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是心湖，还是心眉？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "老僧心眉。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "车上的人是谁？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "出家人不打谎语，车上的除了田七爷外还有一位李檀越。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "好，你将李寻欢交出来，我放你走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "老僧将李某带回少林，也是为了要惩戒于他，檀越与我等同仇敌忾，便不该为难相阻。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "你将李寻欢放出来，我放你走。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "老僧若不答应，又要如何？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "那就先杀你，再杀李寻欢！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我早就想见识见识少林寺的罗汉阵了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快闭气！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "丘独是你杀的？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，丘独一命换李寻欢一命，也算死得不冤了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你在想什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你说他路上绝不会有危险？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "绝不会，有心眉大师和田七保护他，谁敢碰他一根手指？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你要相信我，就放心睡吧，我就在这里，绝不会走的。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "只有一句话。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "什么话？你说！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "你何必来送死？",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "李寻欢，你记着，我……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "好，好，好！小李飞刀，果然刀无虚发，名不虚传。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "你若肯将我的穴道全解开，他就跑不了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我若将你的穴道全都解开，你就要跑了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你只有一双手能动，一柄刀可发，却还是能令伊哭负伤而逃，像你这种人，我对你怎能不特别小心，分外留意？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快，快走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好歹毒的青魔手。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "更歹毒的却是小李飞刀。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "阁下居然肯出手相救，倒出了老僧意料之外。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "我救的不是你而是我自己，你用不着意外，也用不着谢我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我只问他是情愿和我们到少林寺去，还是情愿落在伊哭手里，然后又解开了他双臂的穴道，给了他一柄飞刀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我想这就已足够了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小李神刀……唉，好快的刀！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "我解开你一只手的穴道，是让你拿筷子，不是让你乱动的，我没有塞住你的嘴，是让你吃饭，不是让你乱说话的，你明白了么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "吃饭时没有酒，就像是没有加盐的菜，淡而无味，无趣极了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "有饭给你吃已不错了，我看你就马虎些吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这菜吃不得。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "探花爷若吃不惯这些粗菜，看来就只有挨饿了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "菜中有毒！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "不让你喝酒，你的花样果然来了，我就知道你……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快，快以丹田之气护住心脉。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_lin_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少林僧人",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "师叔是在吩咐我们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "自然是吩咐你们，你们中了毒难道连一点都感觉不出？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_lin_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少林僧人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "中了毒？谁中了毒？……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_lin_seng_ren",
      "speaker_name": "少林僧人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你的脸怎的……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是什么毒？怎地如此厉害？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_dian_huo",
      "text": "你们在菜里下了什么毒？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "笨蛋，若是我下的毒，我早就跑了，还在这里瞧什么热闹？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "就算我们全都被毒死，你也跑不了的，我无论如何都会要你陪着我，我活你也活，我死你也得死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "想不到你对我倒真是深情款款，只可惜你不是个绝色的美人，我对男人又偏偏全无兴趣。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_da_shi_fu",
      "speaker_name": "大师傅",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "大师莫非也想来偷着喝两盅么？欢迎欢迎……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就知道他迟早总会来的。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "谁？你知道下毒的人是谁？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "世上的毒大致可分两种，一种是草木之毒，一种是蛇虫之毒，能自草木中提炼毒药的人较多，能提取蛇虫之毒的人较少，能以蛇虫之毒杀人于无形的，普天之下，也只不过仅有一两人而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你……你说的难道是苗疆'极乐峒'的五毒童子？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我也希望来的不是他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他怎会到中原来了？他来干什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "来找我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "看来你的朋友并不多，仇人却不少。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "仇人倒无妨多多益善，朋友只要一两个便已足够，因为有时朋友比仇人还要可怕得多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "菜中有毒，你是怎么看出来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "我也不知道是怎么看出来的，反正我看出来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这就好像我押牌九一样，我若觉得哪一门要赢，那门就有赢无输，别人若问我怎么会知道的，我也回答不出。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这一路上他吃什么，我们就吃什么。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这馍馍几枚钱一个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "便宜得很，味道也不错，大爷要不要尝尝？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "好，你分给我们几个，晚上我请你喝酒。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "这馍馍里总不会有毒了吧，大师请用。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "李檀樾请。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "想不到两位居然也客气起来了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这馍馍也吃不得。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "但赶车的吃了却没有事。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "他吃得我们却吃不得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "因为极乐童子想毒死的并不是他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你是想害我们挨饿？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "你若不信，为何不试试？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你还敢说这馍馍吃不得？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "还是吃不得。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我偏要吃给你看。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说得不错吧，只可惜毒死的是条狗，不是你。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gan_che_de",
      "speaker_name": "赶车的",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "小人不知道，馍馍是小人方才在那面店里买的。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_gan_che_de",
      "text": "狗都被毒死了，为何未毒死你？莫非是你下的毒？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "你逼他没有用，因为他的确不知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "他不知道谁知道？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "你知道？这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "馍馍里有毒，面汤里却有解药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "早知如此，我们先前为何不吃面？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "你若吃面，毒就在面里了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好在只有一两天就到了，我们拼着两日不吃不喝又何妨？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵然不吃不喝，也未必有用。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他也许就要等到我们又饿得无力时再出手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有个主意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "什么主意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "他要毒死的人既非大师，亦非在下……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "老僧既已答应将此人带回少林，就万万不能让他在半途而死！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "这饼吃不得么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "speaker_name": "李寻欢",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "别人都吃得，惟有我们吃不得，就算一万个人吃了这油煎饼都没有事，但我们一吃，就要被毒死！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xian_sheng",
      "text": "小弟弟，我请你吃饼，你请我吃饽饽，好吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我再给你们一吊钱买糖吃。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 464
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "檀越果然是足智多谋，老僧佩服。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "在下倒不是好吃，但晚上既然还要赶路，就非得吃饱了才有精神，否则半路若又有变，体力不支，怎闯得过去？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "正是如此。",
      "tone": "认同",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "text": "大师请。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_mei_da_shi",
      "speaker_name": "心眉大师",
      "listener": "char_tian_qi",
      "text": "多谢。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": "char_li_xun_huan",
      "text": "这碗饽饽你说吃不吃得？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tian_qi",
      "speaker_name": "田七",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "极乐童子若能先算准那孩子要吃油煎饼，又能算准我会用油饼换他的面，能先在里面下了毒，那么我就算被毒死也心甘情愿。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    }
  ],
